\u00f9y v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh thi c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c thi c\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1eafp s\u1ebfp ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n thi c\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh theo th\u1eddi gian t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng, v\u1edbi thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eeb 30 \u0111\u1ebfn 45 ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17625\/thi-cong-lap-dat-noi-that-phong-khach-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=588.4375\" alt=\"Thi c\u00f4ng l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/539683732b3e4bdf96a5e6749923abdd\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Thi c\u00f4ng l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh<\/em><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ii-mau-thi-cong-biet-thu-hoan-thien-sang-trong-hien-dai\"><span id=\"II_Mau_thi_cong_biet_thu_hoan_thien_sang_trong_hien_dai\">II. M\u1eabu thi c\u00f4ng bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n sang tr\u1ecdng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/4924\/mau-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-khach-hien-dai.jpg?width=700&amp;height=525.4666666666667\" alt=\"M\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/50b85fb922d041c99ef4d4f0c8fe6b99\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>M\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/4947\/thiet-ke-va-thi-cong-noi-that-phong-khach.jpg?width=700&amp;height=525.4666666666667\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1ea7 th\u00f4ng minh cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/4353ab5ebcd84f0aae5bd65c2cdc3036\" \/><\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5